  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gourds up is a Weapon Combining Twinstick Roguelike. You will progress through runs by choosing the next rooms that you will fight in, allowing for more strategy during the run. Players will go through decks of cards fighting through many vegetable based enemies, to beat all of the bosses and achieve victory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get random weapons and upgrades, and just don't die! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.poster.avif?t=1757851344\" width=400 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.webm?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.mp4?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Cinnamon the Pumpkin (And Friends) you will be given sets of cards, which transport you to different hand crafted rooms full of enemies that you will have to beat all of to progress and reach harder and harder rooms. As you go through the runs you will find different types of weapons and gain different types of upgrades to make different loadouts and beat all of the bosses.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each Weapon is able to be combined into each other, adding unique effects and adding an extra layer to all of your builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, don't die, because doing so will send you straight back to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.poster.avif?t=1757851344\" width=400 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.webm?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.mp4?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Weapons</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Upgrades</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Room Choices</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Bosses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Strategy when choosing fights</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Challenge Modes When You Beat The Game for the First Time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Different Characters, Each With an Alternative Skin</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gourds up is a Weapon Combining Twinstick Roguelike. You will progress through runs by choosing the next rooms that you will fight in, allowing for more strategy during the run. Players will go through decks of cards fighting through many vegetable based enemies, to beat all of the bosses and achieve victory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get random weapons and upgrades, and just don't die! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.poster.avif?t=1757851344\" width=400 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.webm?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/cf4735877531d16a70785a4da591dffc.mp4?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Cinnamon the Pumpkin (And Friends) you will be given sets of cards, which transport you to different hand crafted rooms full of enemies that you will have to beat all of to progress and reach harder and harder rooms. As you go through the runs you will find different types of weapons and gain different types of upgrades to make different loadouts and beat all of the bosses.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each Weapon is able to be combined into each other, adding unique effects and adding an extra layer to all of your builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, don't die, because doing so will send you straight back to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.poster.avif?t=1757851344\" width=400 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.webm?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081270/extras/c110bc80c257b4d7714ce4405124b117.mp4?t=1757851344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Features</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Weapons</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Upgrades</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Room Choices</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Bosses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Strategy when choosing fights</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Challenge Modes When You Beat The Game for the First Time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Different Characters, Each With an Alternative Skin</p></li></ul>",
